cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with automatic attribute discovery methods for images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also proposes a metric for evaluating the meaningfulness of attributes, which involves machine learning techniques such as clustering and classification, making it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed metric on three attribute datasets, which suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM).
